{"word":"G737 - ἄρτι - árti - ar'-tee - This day","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄρτι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">árti</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ar'-tee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">This day</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இப்பொழுது, இதுமுதல், இதுவரை - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"just now, this moment"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a derivative of <a href=\"#/G142 - αἴρω - aírō - ah'-ee-ro/142\">G142</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G740 - ἄρτος - ártos - ar'-tos/740\">G740</a>) through the idea of <i>suspension</i>; just <i>now:</i> - this day (hour), hence [-forth], here [-after], hither [-to], (even) now, (this) present.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}